# Imported inside the global { } block in the main Caddyfile.
# Overwritten by scripts/setup_custom_tls.sh:
#   - Let's Encrypt: comments only (automatic HTTPS / ACME enabled)
#   - Custom or self-signed PEM: contains "auto_https disable_certs" so Caddy does not fall back to ACME when a hostname is missing from the certificate SAN (Caddy 2.10+).
